snippet.title: 卡库远古封印 Kaku Ancient Seal 宣传片#1
snippet.description:
"Kaku Ancient Seal" is an open-world action role-playing game based on fantasy ancient themes. Players play a primitive man named Kaku in the game, explores the ancient world with pet, finds the lost temple in the depths of the world, and finally wipes out the story of evil forces saving the world!
steam：https://store.steampowered.com/app/1179580/Kaku_Ancient_Seal/
